elements.name: User upload new course with complete data

steps.name: User already on musiclab website
User click login menu on musiclab website
User already in login page
User input "nagita123@gmail.com" as email, input "adminmentor3" as password and select "Mentor" as role
User click the login button
User will get the pop up message "login success"
User will direct to homepage
User click the profile menu on homepage
User already in profile mentor page
User click Kursus Saya menu on profile page
User will direct to Course page
User click the Upload New Course menu on Course page
User will direct to Upload Kursus page
User click the Choose File button to edit profile picture

User input "Biola Pemula Mahasiswa" as Judul Kursus, select "Basic" on Tingkatan Khusus/Level field, "Khusus untuk pemula tingkat mahasiswa" as Deskripsi Khusus, "Mengetahui kunci dasar biola" as Apa yang akan dipelajari, "Mempunyai Biola sendiri" as Prasyarat Khusus, "Mahasiswa" as Untuk siapa khursus ini, "1000000" as Harga khusus, "1" as duration
User click Upload Kursus button
User will get the pop up message "success make a class"
